high_descs: Turn right and go to a countertop in front of you, behind a sink table, from the right side, and face it.
Pick up a butterknife from the countertop.
Turn around, enter the adjacent room on your left, walk to a curtain between a desk and a sofa, and turn to face the table.
Cut a lemon on the table with the butterknife.
Lean downwards above the desk.
Place the butterknife on the desk.
Lean back upwards above the desk.
Pick up a lemon slice from the desk.
Leave the room, and now go to the sink table but from the opposite side.
Put the lemon slice on the sink table.
anns.task_desc: Place the lemon slice on the sink table in the kitchen.
